Package: clone%type_pkg[perl]
Version: 0.18
Revision: 1
Description: recursively copy perl datatypes
Depends: fink (>= 0.20.1-1), perl%type_pkg[perl]-core
BuildDepends: perl%type_pkg[perl]-core, fink (>= 0.20.2.1-1),
Replaces: clone-pm560, clone-pm561, clone-pm580, clone-pm581, clone-pm584, clone-pm585, clone-pm586

Type: perl(5.6.0 5.6.1 5.8.0 5.8.1 5.8.4 5.8.6)
License: Artistic
Maintainer: Benjamin Reed <clone-pm@fink.racoonfink.com>

Source: mirror:cpan:authors/id/R/RD/RDF/Clone-%v.tar.gz
